===Etymology===
From {{Gr.}} ''rhodo'' (red) + [[-phyta]]

===Proper noun===
'''Rhodophyta'''

#{{botany}}: A [[botanical name]] for a [[taxon]] within [[kingdom]] [[Protista]] that includes the [[red alga]]e. The taxon is traditionally given the [[rank]] of a [[division]].

